Class PhraseFinder.Phrase

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.phrasefinder.PhraseFinder.Phrase
  • Enclosing class:
    PhraseFinder

    public static class PhraseFinder.Phrase
extends java.lang.Object
    Phrase represents an n-gram from the dataset. A phrase consists of a sequence of tokens and metadata.
